<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Darkwick Archive — Tokyo Debunker SSR 카드 랭킹</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0A0912; --bg2:#0E0C17; --panel:#15121F; --panel2:#1B172A;
  --line:rgba(217,167,65,.14); --line2:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
  --ink:#ECE9F5; --mut:#9A93B4; --mut2:#6B6484;
  --gold:#D9A741; --gold-dim:#8f6f2e; --cyan:#6FE0D0;
  --red:#E5484D; --green:#4BC873; --blue:#4C9BF5;
  --s:#F0C560; --a:#C9A0FF; --b:#6FE0D0; --c:#8fa0b8; --d:#6B6484;
  --disp:'Chakra Petch',sans-serif; --body:'Inter',sans-serif; --mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--body);
  font-size:15px;line-height:1.5;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 82% -10%, rgba(217,167,65,.06), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(900px 600px at 8% 0%, rgba(111,224,208,.05), transparent 55%);
  background-attachment:fixed;
}
a{color:inherit}
.wrap{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px}

/* header */
header{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
header::before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:
  repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,.015) 0 1px, transparent 1px 3px);
  pointer-events:none;opacity:.5}
.hd{padding:34px 0 26px;position:relative}
.eyebrow{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.32em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);opacity:.85;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.eyebrow::before{content:"";width:26px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);opacity:.6}
h1{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,54px);line-height:.98;margin:12px 0 6px;letter-spacing:.01em}
h1 .sub{color:var(--gold)}
.tag{color:var(--mut);max-width:640px;font-size:14.5px}
.tag b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
.counts{display:flex;gap:26px;margin-top:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.counts .k{font-family:var(--mono)}
.counts .num{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1}
.counts .lbl{font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut2);margin-top:5px}

/* controls */
.controls{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:40;background:rgba(10,9,18,.82);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line2)}
.ctrl-row{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;padding:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap}
.search{flex:1;min-width:200px;position:relative}
.search input{width:100%;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:10px;color:var(--ink);
  font-family:var(--body);font-size:14px;padding:11px 12px 11px 38px;outline:none}
.search input:focus{border-color:var(--gold-dim)}
.search svg{position:absolute;left:12px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);opacity:.5}
.seg{display:flex;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.seg button{background:transparent;border:0;color:var(--mut);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.03em;padding:9px 13px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
.seg button:hover{color:var(--ink)}
.seg button.on{color:var(--bg);font-weight:700}
.seg.color button.on[data-v="Red"]{background:var(--red)}
.seg.color button.on[data-v="Green"]{background:var(--green)}
.seg.color button.on[data-v="Blue"]{background:var(--blue)}
.seg.stype button.on{background:var(--cyan);color:#05231e}
.seg.sort button.on{background:var(--gold);color:#241a06}
select.sel{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:10px;color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px;padding:9px 12px;cursor:pointer;outline:none}
select.sel:focus{border-color:var(--gold-dim)}
.ghost{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--gold);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.05em;padding:9px 14px;border-radius:10px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;text-transform:uppercase}
.ghost:hover{background:rgba(217,167,65,.08)}
.ghost.on{background:var(--gold);color:#241a06;border-color:var(--gold)}

/* weights panel */
.weights{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .35s ease;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line2)}
.weights.open{max-height:420px}
.weights-in{padding:20px 0 22px}
.weights-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px}
.weights-head h3{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:.04em;margin:0;text-transform:uppercase}
.weights-head p{margin:0;color:var(--mut);font-size:12.5px;max-width:620px}
.wgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:16px}
.wcell label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut);margin-bottom:8px}
.wcell label b{color:var(--gold)}
.wcell input[type=range]{width:100%;accent-color:var(--gold);cursor:pointer}
.wnote{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--mut2);margin-top:14px;font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.7}
.wnote b{color:var(--cyan)}

/* grid */
main{padding:26px 0 70px}
.gridhead{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.gridhead .n{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--mut);letter-spacing:.05em}
.gridhead .n b{color:var(--gold)}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(184px,1fr));gap:16px}
.card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;position:relative;transition:transform .18s,border-color .18s,box-shadow .18s}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:var(--gold-dim);box-shadow:0 14px 34px -18px rgba(217,167,65,.5)}
.card:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:2px}
.imgwrap{position:relative;aspect-ratio:3/4;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg2)}
.imgwrap img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform .3s}
.card:hover .imgwrap img{transform:scale(1.05)}
.imgwrap::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent 45%,rgba(10,9,18,.92) 100%)}
.rankbadge{position:absolute;top:9px;left:9px;z-index:2;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.tier{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:700;font-size:15px;width:26px;height:26px;display:grid;place-items:center;border-radius:7px;color:#120e06;letter-spacing:0}
.tier.S{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFE08A,#E0A650);box-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(240,197,96,.5)}
.tier.A{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#DCC0FF,#B98CFF);color:#1e1030}
.tier.B{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#9DF0E4,#5FD4C4);color:#05231e}
.tier.C{background:#8fa0b8;color:#0c141d}
.tier.D{background:#4b4660;color:#cfc9e0}
.rnum{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);background:rgba(10,9,18,.7);padding:3px 7px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid var(--line2)}
.chips{position:absolute;top:9px;right:9px;z-index:2;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;align-items:flex-end}
.dot{width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:3px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25)}
.dot.Red{background:var(--red)}.dot.Green{background:var(--green)}.dot.Blue{background:var(--blue)}
.stype-pill{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:5px;background:rgba(10,9,18,.72);border:1px solid var(--line2);color:var(--cyan)}
.cinfo{position:absolute;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;z-index:2;padding:10px 11px}
.cchar{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);opacity:.9}
.cname{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;line-height:1.1;margin-top:2px}
.cscore{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;margin-top:7px}
.bar{flex:1;height:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}
.bar i{display:block;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold-dim),var(--gold))}
.sval{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold)}
.empty{grid-column:1/-1;text-align:center;padding:60px 20px;color:var(--mut)}
.empty b{color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--disp);font-size:18px;display:block;margin-bottom:6px}

/* modal */
.overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(5,4,10,.78);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .22s;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;padding:28px 16px;overflow-y:auto}
.overlay.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
.modal{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--panel2),var(--panel));border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;max-width:940px;width:100%;position:relative;transform:translateY(14px) scale(.99);transition:transform .25s;box-shadow:0 40px 90px -30px rgba(0,0,0,.8)}
.overlay.open .modal{transform:none}
.mclose{position:absolute;top:14px;right:14px;z-index:5;background:rgba(10,9,18,.6);border:1px solid var(--line2);color:var(--ink);width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:10px;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;line-height:1;transition:.15s}
.mclose:hover{background:var(--red);border-color:var(--red)}
.mtop{display:grid;grid-template-columns:280px 1fr;gap:0}
.mimg{position:relative;border-radius:18px 0 0 0;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg2)}
.mimg img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}
.mimg .stamp{position:absolute;bottom:12px;left:12px;right:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px}
.mhead{padding:26px 26px 20px;position:relative}
.mrar{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--gold);border:1px solid var(--line);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-transform:uppercase}
.mchar{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut);margin-top:16px}
.mname{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(24px,3.4vw,34px);line-height:1.02;margin:3px 0 0}
.mmeta{display:flex;gap:9px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px}
.mtag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:7px;border:1px solid var(--line2);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:var(--mut)}
.mtag .dot{width:9px;height:9px}
.mtag b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
.mbody{padding:4px 26px 28px}
.sec{margin-top:26px}
.sec>h4{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin:0 0 12px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px}
.sec>h4 .cnt{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--mut2);letter-spacing:0}

/* readout */
.readout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:12px}
.ro{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:11px;padding:13px 14px}
.ro .lbl{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut2)}
.ro .big{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:700;font-size:26px;margin-top:4px;color:var(--ink)}
.ro .big.cy{color:var(--cyan)}.ro .big.go{color:var(--gold)}
.ro .foot{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10.5px;color:var(--mut);margin-top:4px;line-height:1.4}
.mp-orbs{display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.orb{width:15px;height:15px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid var(--line2);background:transparent}
.orb.start{background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%,#9ff0e4,var(--cyan));border-color:var(--cyan)}
.orb.cap{border-color:rgba(111,224,208,.4);border-style:dashed}

/* skill blocks */
.skill{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:11px;padding:14px 15px;margin-bottom:10px}
.skill:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.skill.uniq{border-color:rgba(217,167,65,.35);background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(217,167,65,.06),var(--bg2))}
.sk-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.sk-name{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--ink)}
.sk-awk{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);margin-top:2px}
.sk-awk span{color:var(--mut2)}
.sk-desc{color:var(--mut);font-size:13.5px;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.55}
.sk-desc b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
.sk-stats{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:11px}
.st{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;padding:4px 9px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid var(--line2);color:var(--mut);white-space:nowrap}
.st b{color:var(--ink)}
.st.tu b{color:var(--gold)}
.st.mp-cost b{color:var(--red)}
.st.mp-gain b{color:var(--cyan)}
.st.dmg b{color:var(--ink)}
.st.tgt b{color:var(--ink)}
.st.delay{background:rgba(217,167,65,.08);border-color:rgba(217,167,65,.25)}
.st.delay b{color:var(--gold)}

/* score breakdown */
.brk{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:9px}
.brkrow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:110px 1fr 44px;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.brkrow .rl{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut)}
.brkrow .rb{height:7px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.brkrow .rb i{display:block;height:100%;border-radius:4px}
.brkrow .rv{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;text-align:right;color:var(--ink)}
.total-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:16px}
.total-badge .big-tier{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:700;font-size:34px;width:56px;height:56px;display:grid;place-items:center;border-radius:12px;color:#120e06}
.total-badge .tinfo .tl{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut2)}
.total-badge .tinfo .tv{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:30px;font-weight:700;line-height:1}
.total-badge .tinfo .tv small{font-size:14px;color:var(--mut)}
.total-badge .trank{margin-left:auto;text-align:right}
.total-badge .trank .tl{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mut2)}
.total-badge .trank .tv{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold)}

.method{font-size:12px;color:var(--mut);font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.75;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--line2);border-radius:11px;padding:14px 16px}
.method b{color:var(--cyan)}
.method code{color:var(--gold);background:rgba(217,167,65,.08);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px}

footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line2);padding:26px 0 40px;color:var(--mut2);font-size:12px;font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.7}
footer a{color:var(--gold)}

@media(max-width:680px){
  .mtop{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .mimg{border-radius:18px 18px 0 0;aspect-ratio:16/10}
  .brkrow{grid-template-columns:96px 1fr 40px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
 <div class="wrap hd">
   <div class="eyebrow">TOKYO DEBUNKER · CHARACTER CARD INDEX</div>
   <h1>DARKWICK <span class="sub">ARCHIVE</span></h1>
   <p class="tag">전 <b>SSR</b> 캐릭터 카드를 TU · MP · Speed 전투 메커니즘으로 정량 분석한 랭킹 아카이브. 카드를 눌러 유니크 / 액티브 / 패시브 스킬과 전투 판정을 확인하세요.</p>
   <div class="counts" id="counts"></div>
 </div>
</header>

<div class="controls">
 <div class="wrap">
  <div class="ctrl-row">
    <div class="search">
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
      <input id="q" type="text" placeholder="카드명 · 캐릭터 · 스킬 검색…">
    </div>
    <select class="sel" id="house"></select>
    <div class="seg color" id="colorSeg"></div>
    <div class="seg stype" id="stypeSeg"></div>
    <button class="ghost" id="wtoggle">⚖ 랭킹 가중치</button>
  </div>
  <div class="ctrl-row" style="padding-top:0">
    <span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--mut2);letter-spacing:.1em">SORT</span>
    <div class="seg sort" id="sortSeg"></div>
  </div>
 </div>
 <div class="weights" id="weights">
  <div class="wrap weights-in">
    <div class="weights-head">
      <h3>랭킹 가중치</h3>
      <p>랭킹 점수는 각 카드의 스킬·속도를 다섯 축으로 정규화(0–100)해 가중 평균합니다. 슬라이더를 움직이면 즉시 재정렬됩니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="wgrid" id="wgrid"></div>
    <div class="wnote">
      전투 판정 · <b>진입 지연</b> = ceil((Speed−100)/10) · <b>행동 지연</b> = ceil((스킬 TU−100)/10) · <b>MP</b>는 5로 시작해 0–10 범위, 스킬 사용 시 증감(음수 불가) · 광역(All)은 3체 조우 가정.
    </div>
  </div>
 </div>
</div>

<main>
 <div class="wrap">
   <div class="gridhead">
     <div class="n"><b id="showN">0</b> / <span id="totN">0</span> 카드 표시</div>
     <div class="n" id="sortLbl"></div>
   </div>
   <div class="grid" id="grid"></div>
 </div>
</main>

<footer>
 <div class="wrap">
   데이터 출처: Tokyo Debunker Wiki (커뮤니티 편집, CC BY-SA 4.0). 스탯이 비어 있는 카드는 원본 자료 공백이며 랭킹에서 중앙값·유틸리티로 보정 처리됩니다.<br>
   본 랭킹은 사용자가 정의한 TU/MP/Speed 모델에 근거한 추정치로, 실제 게임 밸런스와 다를 수 있습니다.
 </div>
</footer>

